---
title: Pesto Crumbed Salmon with broccoli and garlicky potato dauphinoise
description: The crispy pesto crumb which coats the salmon in this dish is a savoury revelation, filled with sharp Italian style cheese. The broccoli that accompanies is cooked to tender perfection, with the brightness of the lemon bringing out its natural earthy flavour.
